{"tid":425290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《IU的食物對決》跟粉絲的互動真的好活潑XDD","createTime":"2017-10-05T15:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T16:12:23.000Z","uid":103309,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b58a3b37fe7d7bd03afa5d235d9879d207ec8b","tid":425290,"uid":103309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"一位明星紅不紅有很多原因，跟粉絲的互動更是很重要的一環～畢竟現在網路這麼發達，就算沒事也會中槍啊XDD  而今天要來聊聊的是韓國的IU，雖然也曾登上討厭女星的排行榜的冠軍，不過她在韓國是真的滿紅的，而且也有很多粉絲～最近就看到網友整理了一些IU跟粉絲的食物對決，只能說淘氣的IU在網路世界真的是很活潑啊～～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「出門拍的自拍照要上傳唷」<br />\nIU：「鯛魚燒」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl56Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl56Y.jpg&h=ebf97998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（咦？粉絲不是說要自拍照嗎XDDD）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲（上傳了冰淇淋照）：「想吃齁～？今天也吃了嗎？」<br />\nIU：「我吃了辣炒年糕跟下面這些喔」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl56Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl56Z.jpg&h=65767e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「我好餓喔，上傳一些食物照給我看吧，像之前的鯛魚燒那種」<br />\nIU：「這種嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_a.jpg&h=4d1106af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「哈哈哈哈成功了，我要反擊看看～」<br />\nIU：「反擊！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_c.jpg&h=0f3401d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「聽說二月要去旅行？去玩回來了嗎？有拍了漂亮的風景的話我想拿來當背景圖片^^」<br />\nIU：「無人的公車」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_d.jpg&h=05f108cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「看起來很好吃吧～」<br />\nIU：「對啊」（然後上傳披薩照XDDD）<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_e.jpg&h=c95b0855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「想吃齁想吃齁想吃齁齁齁」<br />\nIU：「方背洞（某地區）的米餅乾都在笑你了」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_Wpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_Wpw.jpg&h=727a0d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「IU姐姐最近吃過的最好吃的東西是什麼啊？顆顆」<br />\nIU：「昨天吃的義大利麵～」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_WqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_WqA.jpg&h=26a3433d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「看起來很好吃吧～～成功！！」<br />\nIU：「很老套欸」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_WqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_WqQ.jpg&h=5a187216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（大家是有多愛傳食物照刺激她啦XDDD）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「IU姐姐你也吃過這個蛋糕嗎～kerker」<br />\nIU：「竟然拿甜點照！那我也用甜點照回妳」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_Wqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_Wqg.jpg&h=19ba28ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「最近吃過最貴的東西是什麼啊？我呢...這傢伙！」（錯字已修正，謝謝網友提醒^^）<br />\nIU：「這傢伙」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_Wqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_Wqw.jpg&h=650119c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「嘿嘿～」<br />\nIU：「拿湯來我也用湯的照片回妳～」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_WrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_WrA.jpg&h=1f2e7ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「如果我拿這張照片的話，你要用什麼反擊呢呵呵」<br />\nIU：「巧克力當然就用巧克力反擊啊～」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_WrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_WrQ.jpg&h=63954ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「冰的話喜歡吃哪一種呢？」<br />\nIU：「蛤，你說冰嗎？」（po了一個看起來更好吃的XDDD）<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_Wrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_Wrg.jpg&h=20371429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼粉絲：「全州的豆腐鍋！！」<br />\nIU：「XX大學的泡菜鍋！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/51/32/p6CVpKSXl5_Wrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F51%2F32%2Fp6CVpKSXl5_Wrw.jpg&h=5c8c2502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哈哈哈IU私下也太可愛了吧～跟大家PK食物照到凌晨三點XDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有跟她PK到的粉絲一定超興奮的吧.......&gt;w&lt;"},{"pid":"0ce7731c7d1911d9c1671addb6e7d6aeeb1c04be","tid":425290,"uid":5834,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"係 我都好撚興奮 一張圖都睇唔到<br />\n去舊登學識貼圖先返黎啦"},{"pid":"084aa037eb4fc61286819f1152f75ed603343c9c","tid":425290,"uid":71624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 我都好撚興奮 一張圖都睇唔到<br />\n去舊登學識貼圖先返黎啦</blockquote><br />\n我睇到喎"},{"pid":"2df9ab6ec8159f58f1cc2c80e04175eb8e407739","tid":425290,"uid":6694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"死圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0415422bad9795daaa60358a6fa5b7f8b71d9981","tid":425290,"uid":87818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"睇到"},{"pid":"9d885ed4d4b61b97679689504a03fa07a3d6fab4","tid":425290,"uid":142713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"睇到<br />\niu bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023c800f77db4fd298ad3499b0cbe44670fa54e5","tid":425290,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75988af8186a4fca83929894bc8f9b67d816aa28","tid":425290,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\nIU曾患暴食症每次「嘔吐才停止吃」"},{"pid":"7fce521761dd25bf1b365536753fb090185e8a5e","tid":425290,"uid":46729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 我都好撚興奮 一張圖都睇唔到<br />\n去舊登學識貼圖先返黎啦</blockquote><br />\n你盲架？"}]}